<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">首数差1、尾数和是11的两个两位数相乘时，可先将乘数减1后，按“首差尾合法（二）”相乘，然后再加上被乘数，此数即为所求之积。可利用公式</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">A×B=A×(B-1)+A=(10a×10a-b×b)+(10a+b)</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算，其中A、B分别是两个因数，且A>B；a、b分别是大数十位、个位上的数字。</Run>
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">62×59=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 62×59</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=62×(59-1)+62</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=62×58+62</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=60×60-2×2+62</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=3600-4+62</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=3658</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>